However, on[$ Cucurbita pepo#Plant*], differences in host responses to inoculation with the [$ZYMV#Virus*] isolates from different phylogenetic groups were observed.
Although the host range of the 13 isolates tested was similar, their biological properties on different hosts were slightly different from the [$ZYMV#Virus*] isolates characterized in other countries.
The results of the pathotype test showed that the 13 [$ZYMV#Virus*] isolates were classified as pathotype 0.
